Practical number : 02
Title: Introduction to java programming.
Date & Time :20.03.2025 10.30a.m - 12.30pm

Objectives : To understand basic syntax and structure of a java program.

Theory / Concept :Java programs consist of classes & methods, Every application has a main method where execution begins.
   	 Explanation:
		public: Allows access from outside the class.
		static: Enables execution without creating an object.
		void: Indicates no return value.
		String[] args: Holds command-line arguments.

Algorithm :
     Step1:START
     Step2:Import the necessary package (import it.*;
                                         import it.hons.*;
                                         import amc.*;).
     Step3:Define a class named [FirstYear(it,amc),SecondYear,FourthYear,App].
     Step4:Inside the class, create the main method.
     Step5:PRINT using System.out.println().
     Step6:END

Source code :

//App.java

  import it.*;
  import it.hons.*;
  import amc.*;
  
  class App{
  	public static void main(String[] ar){
  		it.FirstYear sy=new it.FirstYear();
  		amc.FirstYear syi=new amc.FirstYear();
  		SecondYear si=new SecondYear();
  		ForthYear itHons=new ForthYear();
  		
  		sy.display();
  		syi.display();
  		si.display();
  		itHons.display();
    	}
    }

//FirstYear.java(it)

package it;

public class FirstYear{
	public void display(){
		System.out.println("Hi from FirstYear in package it");
	}
}

//ForthYear.java(hons)

package it.hons;

public class ForthYear{
	public void display(){
		System.out.println("Hi from ForthYear in package it.hons");
	}
}

//FirstYear.java(amc)

package amc;

public class FirstYear{
	public void display(){
		System.out.println("Hi from FirstYear AMC in package amc");
	}
}

//SecondYear.java(amc)

package amc;

public class SecondYear{
	public void display(){
		System.out.println("Hi from SecondYear in package amc");
	}
}

Output : Hi from FirstYear in package it
         Hi from FirstYear AMC in package amc
         Hi from SecondYear in package amc
         Hi from ForthYear in package it.hons

Observation : Without importing other 4 classes, the main class file ("App.java") won't work.

Conclusion :I learnt about the behaviour of classes in java programming.
